<HEADLINE>
FT  22 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Trafford Park rises to Pounds 2.44m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Turnover of Trafford Park Estates, the property investment, management and
development concern, edged ahead from Pounds 4.87m to Pounds 4.98m and
pre-tax profits expanded to Pounds 2.44m for the six months ended December
31 1993, compared with Pounds 1.74m.
Earnings per share were 2.413p, against 1.72p, while the interim dividend is
lifted to 0.95p (0.85p) - last year's final payment was 1.95p from pre-tax
profits of Pounds 4.12m.
The directors stated that the general outlook for the full year, and
long-term prospects for growth, were promising with further increases in
rental income anticipated.
