</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Khmer Rouge soldiers and civilian supporters flee into Thailand yesterday
after Cambodian government troops captured the Khmer Rouge headquarters of
Pailin. But guerrilla units still control hilltop positions around Pailin
from which they can shell government forces.
