<HEADLINE>
FT  19 MAR 94 / World News in Brief: UK to press for Ulster peace
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
British ministers are preparing to exploit the St Patrick's Day call from
President Bill Clinton for Sinn Fein and the IRA to accept the Downing
Street declaration. Page 6; The fight goes on, Page 9
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
